data.description: Welcome to your new home! This property perfectly sits on a large lot that backs to open space. This quiet neighborhood is close to Old Town and surrounded by easy access via i25. Offering a mostly unfinished basement with a walk-out offers room to grow with rough-ins for a bathroom, full radon mitigation, and a paid off solar geothermal heating/cooling unit. Don't wait to see this beautifully updated home!
